'''BN Radio''' is a [[Bosnia]]n commercial radio station, broadcasting from [[Bijeljina]].

'''BN Radio''' began broadcasting in 1995. and it was formatted as [[Variety (radio)|Variety]] radio station with [[Turbo-folk|Folk or Turbo-folk music]], talk shows and news. [[RTV BN]] is the owner of the BN Radio,<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.rtvbn.com/televizija/o-nama/ |title= About Us: RTV BN |publisher= RTV BN |date=  |accessdate= 2016-02-20 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130926190954/http://www.rtvbn.com/televizija/o-nama/ |archive-date= 26 September 2013 |dead-url= yes |df= dmy-all }}</ref> together with other 3 TV channels (Analog [[BN Televizija]] and Cable BN Televizija, [[BN Music (television channel)|BN Music]]) and [[BN Music]] record label.

==Frequencies==
