{{Infobox prepared food | name = Maraq | image = | caption = | alternate_name = | country = [[Somalia]] | region = | creator = | course = [[lunch]] or [[dinner]] | type = | served = | main_ingredient = [[Olive oil]], [[vegetables]], [[water]] | variations = | calories = | other = }}
'''Maraq''' is a Somali [[soup]] dish. There are many variations, including that made of pumpkin,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.somalikitchen.com/maraq-bocor-pumpkin-soup.html/|title=Maraq Bocor (Pumpkin Soup) - The Somali Kitchen|website=Somalikitchen.com|accessdate=3 September 2018}}</ref> a chicken variation,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mysomalifood.com/chicken-soup-maraq-digaag/|title=Chicken Soup : Maraq Digaag - My Somali Food|date=8 August 2011|website=Mysomalifood.com|accessdate=3 September 2018}}</ref> a goat meat variation,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mysomalifood.com/maraq-fahfah-somali-soup/|title=Maraq Fahfah : Somali Soup - My Somali Food|date=24 May 2009|website=Mysomalifood.com|accessdate=3 September 2018}}</ref>
